name: CelebritySalaries
0:
”Alexa, ask Celebrity Salaries about how much a celebrity gets paid”
”Alexa, open Celebrity Salaries and tell me a celebrity salary”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: celebrity salaries
des:
This celebrity salaries skill will tell you the yearly salary of a random celebrity. Actors, athletes and musicians are all included. Currently, you can only learn the salary of a RANDOM celebrity and cannot ask for a specific name, but updates are being planned.

Just ask something like "Alexa, ask celebrity salaries how much a celebrity made" or "give me another salary from celebrity salaries".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
